I"È<h2 id="details">Details</h2>

<p>Servings: 4 with sufficient brown rice
Capicums: 2
Capsicum podi: 3 tsp
onion: 2 medium
garlic cloves: 2-3 medium</p>

<h2 id="method">Method</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Fry the onions and garlic in oil</li>
  <li>2-3 tsp of capsicum powder</li>
  <li>
    <p>keep aside</p>
  </li>
  <li>fry chopped capsicum</li>
  <li>
    <p>wait till it softens</p>
  </li>
  <li>grind all together with some water and salt as needed</li>
</ul>

